      "file_path": "kubernetes/sdnc/values.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 343,
      "message": "I would disagree. The \"unauthenticated\" prefix is a left over from AAF that was being used by DCAE and DMaaP Message Router. The topic names unfortunately cannot be used but the consumer group can be changed to something specific to the calling application. This is helpful for tracing logs.",
